<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Afmin records further H1 loss, no div.</title>
<headline>Afmin records further H1 loss, no div.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Half yr ended June 30, 1996</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)     0.16 loss    vs    11.49 loss</p>
<p>    Attrib loss	     4.21	   vs    3.05</p>
<p>    Pre-tax loss	    4.21	   vs    14.05</p>
<p>    Tax			  nil	   vs    0.04</p>
<p>    Interest paid	   0.02	   vs    4.81</p>
<p>    Turnover		  0.78	   vs    52.29</p>
<p>Full name: Afmin Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said it had achieved a near break even position on disposal of its granite and gold interests and further restructuring. It predicted a return to profitability within the next six to 12 months.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
</text>
